sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SA as Stress App
    participant PR as Prometheus
    participant AM as Alertmanager
    participant API as AI Engine API
    participant MON as Monitor Agent
    participant RCA as RCA Agent
    participant REM as Remediation Agent
    participant K8S as Kubernetes API
    participant REP as Report Agent
    participant DB as Incident Store
    participant DIS as Discord

    SA->>PR: High CPU behavior
    PR->>AM: Firing alert
    AM->>API: POST /alerts

    API->>MON: Collect context
    MON->>PR: Query metrics
    MON->>RCA: Enriched signals

    RCA->>RCA: LLM + RAG reasoning
    RCA->>REM: Proposed action + confidence

    alt Guardrails pass
        REM->>K8S: Execute safe action\n(restart or scale)
        K8S-->>REM: Action result
    else Guardrails block
        REM-->>REP: Mark as blocked or fallback
    end

    REM->>REP: Final remediation summary
    REP->>DB: Persist incident + report
    REP->>DIS: Send notification
